Amazon has launched its Prime Day sale, with hundreds of products available at discounted prices. The sale launched in the US last night, and the deals will run for the next 25 hours. Products on offer include a range of Amazon’s devices, such as the Kindle, Echo, and Fire TV. Other electronic items and gadgets from big brands are also on offer. It must be noted that sale is exclusively available to Amazon Prime members, and that certain products may not ship to South Africa directly. A selection of the deals are detailed below.     